original_title: Brooklyn: Fulton Street - New Jersey Avenue
text:
Fulton Street, at the N.W. corner of New Jersey Ave., showing the home of John S. Andrews in 1873. (This house originally stood on the east side of Pennsylvania Ave., between Fulton Street and Jamaica Ave).

1922.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
